{
  "texts": [
    "However, literature review studies on landslide risk assessment and economic losses are unavailable.",
    "Nevertheless, recent studies highlight the importance of incorporating the economic assessment of landslides from a holistic perspective to measure the global impact of a disaster.",
    "Compared to the literature reviews, this study examines recent trends and new researches concerning the integration of landslide risk assessment and its economic losses-an aspect overlooked",
    "in prior analyses.",
    "Employing innovative tools like VOSviewer and Bibliometrix, this research identifies and contributes to current trends, serving as a foundation for future studies."
  ]
}